Sokoban game in python with simple solver built on David Moreno's sokoban code.

Key         Action
←↑↓→    Move left, up, down, right
n/p     Next/previous level
N/P     Next/previous unsolved level
>/<     Next/previous world
q       Quit
r       Re-start
s       If no solution, solve from the current state;
        space   pause solve
        esc     exit solve
S       Solve from the initial state, even if a solution exists
R       Replay solution
u/U     Undo/Re-do

Debug
^a      show NO_BOX squares
^h      print heuristic
^n      print neighbors
^s      print solution string
